        </div>
        <div class="flip-card-back">
          <h2>Will Barry</h2>
          <p>Over 10 years of full-stack experience. Passionate about mentoring new developers. Contact at WillBarry@spillstudies.co.uk</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flip-card">
      <div class="flip-card-inner">
        <div class="flip-card-front">
          <img src="/images/professor 2.jpg" alt="" />
          <h2>Dasha Homry</h2>
          <p>Data Science</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flip-card-back">
          <h2>Dasha Homry</h2>
          <p>Specializes in machine learning and Python. Loves simplifying complex topics. Contact at DashaHomry@spillstudies.co.uk</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flip-card">
      <div class="flip-card-inner">
        <div class="flip-card-front">
          <img src="/images/professor 3.jpg" alt="" />
          <h2>Bogdan Lindu</h2>
