        </div>
        <div class="flip-card-back">
          <h2>Bogdan Lindu</h2>
          <p>Published author and creative coach. Helps students express their unique voice. Contact at BogdanLindu@spillstudies.co.uk</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flip-card">
      <div class="flip-card-inner">
        <div class="flip-card-front">
          <img src="/images/instructor 4.jpg" alt="Alan Reyes" />
          <h2>Alan Reyes</h2>
